<h1>Original Art - $40 for select originals!</h1>
<h2 class="postcat_all_about_brad postauthor_Guigar">in <a href="/search/index.html?search=forums;q=category%3A%22All%20About%20Brad%22;by=date">All About Brad</a> by <a href="/users/Guigar/">Guigar</a></h2>
<h3 class="date">Thursday, December 27, 2012 - 12:00 AM</h3>
<div class="content">
    <br><br>

<img src="/images/blogart/original_art_sample_sale.jpg"><br><br>

From now until January 1, 2013, I'm offering any of the available originals that ran after Sept. 3, 2012, for $40 apiece. That half-off the already-reduced convention price!<br><br>

<font color="red"><i>Unfortunately, none of the Saturday strips are available.</i></font><br><br>

<b>Just use the ADD TO CART button below.</b> Simply enter the date of the original you would like and process your payment. In the event that the original you've chosen isn't available, I'll get in touch and you can either (a) pick another or (b) have your entire payment refunded.<br><br>

Signed originals are produced on heavy bristol board with archival ink. They measure about 13 inches wide by 4 inches tall.<br><br>

While you're at it, you might want to check out the <a href="http://www.evil-comic.com/store/secret/">deep discounts on Evil Inc graphic novels that also expire on New Year's Day.</a><br><br>


