<div class="dh_post" id="stains_9447">
<h1>Courting Disaster: Nov. 30, 2012</h1>
<h2 class="postcat_courting_disaster postauthor_Guigar">in <a href="/search/index.html?search=forums;q=category%3A%22Courting%20Disaster%22;by=date">Courting Disaster</a> by <a href="/users/Guigar/">Guigar</a></h2>
<h3 class="date">Friday, November 30, 2012 - 12:00 AM</h3>
<div class="content">
    <a href="http://www.courting-disaster.com"><img src="/images/blogart/cd20121130_thumb.jpg" hspace="20" align="right"></a> <br><br>Courting Disaster is my weekly relationship-advice comic where a reader asks a question, and <b>you</b> give the advice.<br><br>

<br><i>A reader writes...</i></font><br><br>

Q. <b>I'm an 18-year-old girl and I have been single all of my life never been kissed or whatever. It's not that I'm really ugly or anything, because I got offered a job as a model (not that I use tons of make-up). And I'm successful as a singer/actress. But somehow I can only fall in love with guys who already have a girlfriend -- or guys who live in another country (like the one I met during gaming years ago and chat with online). What should I do?!</b><br><br>

<i>Don't answer here</i>... go to the <a href="http://www.courting-disaster.com">Courting Disaster site to offer your advice.</a><br>
</div>
